Cottageville Elementary:
We assume that everything needs
to be provided

00:46.413 --> 00:47.881 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
here.

00:47.915 --> 00:50.350 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
