President-elect Donald Trump
has penciled in two more names
on his White

01:14.641 --> 01:16.410 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
House staff sheet.

01:16.443 --> 01:19.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
He announced today that Thomas
Bossert will
be assistant to the president
for homeland

01:19.746 --> 01:21.515 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
security and counterterrorism.

01:21.548 --> 01:24.151 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
