04:13.420 --> 04:16.890 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: It was the
role of a lifetime,
and for Carrie Fisher, playing
Princess Leia

04:16.923 --> 04:19.192 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Organa defined much of her life.

04:19.226 --> 04:22.462 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
As she once said: "I have always
been in 'Star
Wars.'

04:22.496 --> 04:24.564 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
I have never not been in 'Star
Wars.'"

04:24.598 --> 04:29.469 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
