04:31.338 --> 04:33.840 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CARRIER FISHER: I didn't want to
be different
than other people, and that's
what celebrities

04:33.874 --> 04:34.841 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
