04:34.875 --> 04:36.776 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So being a celebrity kid, that's
the dichotomy.

04:36.810 --> 04:39.179 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
You want to fit in, not stick
out.

04:39.212 --> 04:40.447 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHARLIE ROSE, Host, "The Charlie
Rose Show":
With other celebrity kids.

04:40.480 --> 04:42.782 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CARRIER FISHER: No, I wasn't
just around celebrity
kids.

04:42.816 --> 04:45.886 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHARLIE ROSE: Oh, you wanted to
fit in with
other normal people who weren't
celebrity

04:45.919 --> 04:46.887 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
kids?

04:46.920 --> 04:47.888 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
CARRIER FISHER: Yes.

04:47.921 --> 04:49.623 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
My fantasy was to be normal.

04:49.656 --> 04:53.193 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Fisher began
her own career
in "Shampoo" with Warren Beatty
in 1975.

04:53.226 --> 05:00.167 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
