She won notice as a screenwriter
and author,
too, depicting her struggle with
drug addiction

05:30.697 --> 05:36.570 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
in 1987's "Postcards From the
Edge," her semi-autobiographical
novel and later movie.

05:36.603 --> 05:37.571 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
ACTRESS: I'm not doing any
drugs.

