06:32.659 --> 06:41.901 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We begin with politics tonight
and new questions
surrounding president-elect
Donald Trump's

06:41.935 --> 06:43.570 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
