gets a free
breakfast and lunch.

29:35.007 --> 29:41.079 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The school's 137 students come
from the surrounding
neighborhoods, including three
nearby trailer

29:41.113 --> 29:42.914 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
parks.

29:42.948 --> 29:47.853 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Principal LeMasters figures
about a third
of her students do not live with
their biological

29:47.886 --> 29:50.822 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
