principal of
a school, running a school?

29:54.726 --> 29:59.197 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TRACY LEMASTERS: We assume that
everything
needs to be provided here.

29:59.231 --> 30:03.769 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So that means, if they need
clothes, we're
going to give them clothes.

30:03.802 --> 30:06.304 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If they need food, we're going
to get them
food.

30:06.338 --> 30:09.307 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You know, they need love, we're
giving them
the hug.

30:09.341 --> 30:15.247 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: School counselor
Robin Corbin
meets with kids three days a
week.

30:15.280 --> 30:16.381 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's not enough.

30:16.415 --> 30:18.884 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
