30:37.502 --> 30:39.705 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
What are you hoping to
accomplish with this
program?

30:39.738 --> 30:44.342 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ROBIN CORBIN, School Counselor:
Just someone
else in their life that they can
depend on.

30:44.376 --> 30:47.713 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That was one of the main things
that we ask
of these mentors, is that they
be reliable

30:47.746 --> 30:49.414 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
and dependable.

30:49.448 --> 30:52.317 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
If they say they're going to be
here Tuesday
11:30, please be here Tuesday
11:30.

30:52.350 --> 30:55.520 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
And they have been fantastic
with that.

30:55.554 --> 30:59.524 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's something that these
children don't
have and don't see, an adult
that they can

30:59.558 --> 31:01.359 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
depend on.

31:01.393 --> 31:05.097 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: And like many school
districts
nationwide, this one
participates in a national

31:05.130 --> 31:09.434 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
drug prevention education week,
holding an
essay and poster contest.

31:09.468 --> 31:12.471 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: Next, we will have our
essay award
presentation.

31:12.504 --> 31:19.144 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA STARK: And among the
winners, Briana
Sotomayor, whose essay spoke
volumes.

31:19.177 --> 31:20.579 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Do you mind reading us what you
wrote?

31:20.612 --> 31:21.580 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRIANA SOTOMAYOR: Sure.

31:21.613 --> 31:22.581 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
LISA STARK: Is that OK?

31:22.614 --> 31:23.582 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRIANA SOTOMAYOR: Sure.

31:23.615 --> 31:24.716 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
LISA STARK: OK.

31:24.750 --> 31:25.584 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I'm going to give you -- this is
your winning
essay.

31:25.617 --> 31:26.585 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
BRIANA SOTOMAYOR: OK.

31:26.618 --> 31:28.019 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
"A Better Life."

31:28.053 --> 31:30.655 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
"There once was this woman who
was on drugs,
and I was her daughter.

31:30.689 --> 31:32.491 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
