place in Africa
and is this amazing superhero.

36:49.040 --> 36:51.876 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
It's about a lot of stuff that
we're talking
about now.

36:51.910 --> 36:52.877 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
It's about race.

36:52.911 --> 36:53.878 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It's about power.

36:53.912 --> 36:56.981 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It's about just trying to change
the world.

36:57.015 --> 36:58.349 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
And it's fascinating.

36:58.383 --> 37:02.187 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, I am a big Black Panther
fan, even though
I wasn't as a child.

37:02.220 --> 37:03.321 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I didn't read comic books.

37:03.354 --> 37:04.322 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
