37:04.355 --> 37:06.124 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
But I have turned a corner.

37:06.157 --> 37:11.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DANIEL PINK: "Mad" magazine is
like one of
my few formative experiences,
absolutely.

37:11.696 --> 37:15.834 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
"Mad" magazine teaches a whole
generation
of people to be irreverent
toward power.

37:15.867 --> 37:17.435 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
