37:17.469 --> 37:20.472 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JACQUELINE WOODSON: It's so
true, that question
of, you can really do that?

37:20.505 --> 37:23.274 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DANIEL PINK: Yes, and get away
with it, and
you actually make money it from
too.

37:23.308 --> 37:24.275 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

37:24.309 --> 37:25.477 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: All right.

37:25.510 --> 37:27.145 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Daniel Pink, number three?

37:27.178 --> 37:29.747 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DANIEL PINK: So, I have got this
